l Energy Required: 5,736<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbBurn<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 12 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 3.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 97<br><br><color=#00008B>During Ability Effect:<\/color><br>Damage: 665 \\u00d7 4 hits<br>Skill Energy Required: 5,736<br>Special Effects:<br>\\u30fbBurn<br>\\u3000\\u3000Lasts 12 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Triggers every 3.9 seconds<br>\\u3000\\u3000Damage: 97<br><\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div>\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/756879fc2f94c1df98ecd39bf3dd90ae2.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>HP +15%<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIncreases HP by 15%.<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n\\n\\t<div class=\\"exAbility explanation\\">\\n\\t\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Chain Co-ability<\/div>\\n\\t\\t<dl>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/87595b7438e74e5502d8b830d6bd16832.png\\"><\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<span>(Flame) Dragon\'s Claws VI<\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dt>\\n\\t\\t\\t<dd>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tIf a team member is attuned to Flame:<br>each shapeshift increases their strength<br>(up to three times per quest).<br>Benefits your whole team.\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\/dd>\\n\\t\\t<\/dl>\\n\\t<\/div>\\n<div class=\\"ability explanation\\">\\n\\t<div class=\\"title\\">Abilities<\/div>\\n\\t<dl><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/b5b8a0971c2940faccafb60e2bb060ab2.png\\"><\/span><span>Flamewyrm\'s Nature III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to burning by 100%.<br>When Mym is hit by an attack that would have<br>inflicted her with burn, her strength is increased<br>by 15% for 10 seconds. After activating, this buff<br>will not activate again for 15 seconds.<br><br>Also, when shapeshifting for the first time, Mym<br>will transform into Brunhilda regardless of what<br>dragon she is equipped with, her strength will<br>increase by 15% for the remainder of the quest,<br>and the skill Flames of Passion will be powered<br>up for the remainder of the quest. The second time<br>onwards, she will transform into High Brunhilda<br>instead, and her attack rate while shapeshifted<br>will increase by 15%.<br><br>In addition, using a skill will grant Mym a<br>strength amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of three. After this amp is granted, this ability<br>will not grant it again for 30 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/28c0b4387ec47573e89a7e34a452fa012.png\\"><\/span><span>Flamewyrm\'s Defiance III<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun and sleep by 100%.<br>When Mym is hit by an attack that would have<br>stunned or put her to sleep, the skill gauge for<br>the Dragon Claw skill fills by 50%, and her<br>strength is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>these effects cannot be activated again by the<br>same affliction for 15 seconds.<\/div><\/dd><dt><span><img src=\\"https:\/\/dragalialost.akamaized.net\/attached\/information\/images\/f95daa91eaca6e0d41a23320398a9e792.png\\"><\/span><span>Dragon Time +25%<\/span><\/dt><dd><div>Extends shapeshift time by 25%.<\/div><\/dd><\/dl><\/div><\/div><\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Notes:<\/div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.<\/div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.<\/div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1645941600,"prev_article_id":"2812","next_article_id":"2874","image_path":"","update_time":1645674930}}}'